The paper deals with the design of secure relay beamforming over cognitive radio channels, which involves information theory, communication and networking, and signal processing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.IT (Information Theory), followed by cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), cs.MM (Multimedia), and cs.SI (Signal and Image Processing).
